d and hence the\nrotor torque load, so that the rotor tip speed quickly reaches the optimum\nvalue for the anticipated wind speed. This ratio of rotor tip speed to wind\nspeed is known to be critical in wind power applications. The wind to load\nenergy efficiency of the proposed method was shown to be superior to two other\nmethods; the classical maximum power point tracking method and a generator\ncontrolled by deep deterministic policy gradient (DDPG) method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Sep 2022 22:21:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 12 Mar 2023 14:11:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-14"}
