d amplification is always realized\nin the metal-enriched ACHs regardless of the initial magnetic field strength,\nwhich affects the DCBH formation criterion. In addition, we find a\nqualitatively different trend from the previous unmagnetized simulations in\nthat the mass growth rate is maximal for the extremely metal-poor ACHs with\n$Z/Z_\\odot = 10^{-5}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2022 05:46:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Jun 2023 13:44:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-05"}
