indings that we believe would be very valuable\nto the FM community, paving the way towards real-world application of FMs for\npractical expert tasks currently 'overlooked' by standard benchmarks focusing\non common objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2022 08:47:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2022 14:18:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-20"}
