uming a fixed atmospheric\ncomposition and no gas pressure confinement by the stellar wind. Using the same\nprocedure, we constrain the temperatures and mass-loss rates of WASP-69 b,\nWASP-52 b, HAT-P-11 b, HAT-P-18 b and WASP-107 b.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2022 09:41:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
