ordan representation theorem and similar classification\nfor the analytic functions on the unit closed disk as multiplication operators\non a weighted Hardy space of polynomial growth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2022 14:48:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2022 02:49:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 28 Apr 2023 14:53:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-01"}
